{"tid":219229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大公報記者盧永賢又撞傷人o勒","createTime":"2017-04-27T05:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T15:08:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6abcf4ccee61a5cc3885be74b09deed4c19840","tid":219229,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"<del><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%A0%B1%E7%8B%97%E4%BB%94%E9%9A%8A-%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88-%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%258B%2597%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%259A%258A-%25E7%258B%2599%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AA%2594%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2598%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=a0235dcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%258B%2597%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%259A%258A-%25E7%258B%2599%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AA%2594%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2598%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=2928eefc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%A0%B1%E7%8B%97%E4%BB%94%E9%9A%8A-%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88-%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83/</a></del><br />\n<br />\n四月二十三日，《消失的檔案》於灣仔溫莎公爵社會服務大廈，與社區院線合辦致謝場。<br />\n<br />\n2017/4/26 &mdash; 21:33<br />\n<br />\n社區院線兩名成員交代經過。兩個臨時入場，沒留下資料的女人，在放映結束後要求訪問羅恩惠。羅導拒絕，希望另行約談。但兩人沒理會，逕自舉機拍攝，追問羅導。現場觀眾不忿被拍，與二人爭論。<br />\n<br />\n及後羅導離開放映場地，走到電梯大堂，兩女人繼續狙擊。成員要求交代身份，二人自稱大公報記者，曾亮出記者證，但僅一晃而過，不欲人知姓甚名誰。<br />\n<br />\n其中一成員說，羅導一直站著與她們理論，但為免繼續糾纏，她保護羅導入升降機，擋在電梯門前，阻止兩人尾隨。<br />\n<br />\n兩女人即行樓梯到地下。身在樓下的另一成員，見證兩人與另一男人，為狙擊羅導奪路而出，在走廊與《檔案》的義工爭執。男人表現兇惡，似欲打人。眾人紛紛舉機警告：「咪亂嚟呀，影住你架！」但他為奪路，推義工到牆上，令其手臂受傷流血。<br />\n<br />\n由於紀錄片的觀眾和義工，不少都是記者出身，他們清楚指出，兩女人都是前《壹週刊》員工；而男人就是跟蹤過梁天琦，繼而動武的盧永賢。<br />\n<br />\n前《蘋果日報》的記者這樣形容盧永賢，「認真：小心姓盧，永遠激怒人，然後影你。」"},{"pid":"753c4f63089b5a467c8adc9133cfb0123ca3be08","tid":219229,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"25d0551072e0be8235670c7f633c490f81323d38","tid":219229,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:13:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前《蘋果日報》的記者這樣形容盧永賢，「認真：小心姓盧，永遠激怒人，然後影你。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n難道毒果妓者唔係？<br />\n<br />\n天下妓者一樣黑啦"},{"pid":"a72e71e94c43fd62660fd1a6682e179e01d5165a","tid":219229,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"乞衣狗"},{"pid":"6093f90c4fc84bdad0d609c69817ec2bda0a7f82","tid":219229,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bf9f8dba0754c742eeb3e838a9cc6ea1fb6809a","tid":219229,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9316f98fdb2c7f230e1ba7c8a18fe013174ba9f3","tid":219229,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"盧記者又上鏡了"},{"pid":"086f6ee469c2c067fcd731bdf370bbac73c55c2d","tid":219229,"uid":109364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:07:11.000Z","msg":"報警啦"},{"pid":"d06e7ea736fda6f4a37998b94988cfe43d1d0c11","tid":219229,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72653ace6e8fe92d5b67d6d64970de2d55ba6234","tid":219229,"uid":59690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>禍必及妻女，又要召喚</blockq